Reicast is a Sega Dreamcast emulator.

 http://reicast.com/
 http://reicast.com/forums/index.php?topic=72.0 <- Getting started
 https://github.com/reicast/reicast-emulator



 https://launchpad.net/~random-stuff/+archive/ubuntu/ppa
  sudo add-apt-repository ppa:random-stuff/ppa ; 
  sudo apt update ; 
  sudo apt install reicast reicast-joyconfig ; 



 Config dir is: $HOME/.config/reicast/
 Data dir is:   $HOME/.local/share/reicast/



 https://github.com/RetroPie/RetroPie-Setup/wiki/Dreamcast
 https://www.loveroms.com/extras/dreamcast-bios.php


